==网络和对等策略==
该公司在其全球网络中拥有超过144个PoP<ref>{{cite web |url=http://he.net/peering.html |title=Hurricane Electric Exchange Point Information |publisher=HE.net |accessdate=2016-08-30 |archive-date=2009-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090421200720/http://he.net/peering.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://bgp.he.net/report/exchanges#_participants |title=Internet Exchange Report - Exchange Partcipants (BGP Toolkit) |publisher=BGP.HE.net |accessdate=2016-08-30 |archive-date=2016-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604003103/http://bgp.he.net/report/exchanges#_participants |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，该公司网络和多达6340个其它网络交换IP数据<ref>{{cite web |url=http://bgp.he.net/AS6939 |title=AS6939 Hurricane Electric, Inc. (BGP Toolkit) |publisher=BGP.HE.net |accessdate=2016-08-30 |archive-date=2011-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110921081818/http://bgp.he.net/AS6939 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。该公司目标将其对等网络数量增加的超过一万个的规模以及加入超过150个[[互联网|互联网]][[交换中心|交换中心]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.carpif.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/CarPIF-2016-Walt-Wollny.pdf#page=26 |page=26 |publisher=The Caribbean Peering and Interconnection Forum (CPIF)|author=Walt Wollny (Director Interconnection Strategy) |title=100 Internet Exchange Points And Beyond! |quote=Next milestone 150 Internet Exchanges }}</ref>
根据Euro-IX的说法，该公司是世界上最大的交换中心参与者，其参与的交换中心包括了所有73个Euro-IX的交换中心<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.euro-ix.net/tools/asn-database/?tool=common |title=ASNs present at 20 or more IXPs |publisher=euro-ix.net |access-date=2016-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115121/https://www.euro-ix.net/tools/asn-database/?tool=common |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

===IPv6 网络===
该公司运营了世界上以对等数目计算的最大IPv6网络。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://bgp.potaroo.net/v6/as6447/bgp-as-adj.txt | title = AS's ordered by AS Adjacency | author = Geoff Huston | accessdate = 2016-08-30 | archive-date = 2012-03-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120321025034/http://bgp.potaroo.net/v6/as6447/bgp-as-adj.txt | dead-url = no }}</ref>其中大多数是原生IPv6对等会话。该公司也提供免费IPv6隧穿服务<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.thewhir.com/web-hosting-news/hurricane-electric-launches-premium-ipv6-tunnel-broker-service|title = Hurricane Electric Launches Premium IPv6 Tunnel Broker Service|author = Henderson, Nicole|date = June 6, 2011|work = Web Host Industry Review|accessdate = 2016-08-30|archive-date = 2012-11-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121117085405/http://www.thewhir.com/web-hosting-news/hurricane-electric-launches-premium-ipv6-tunnel-broker-service|dead-url = no}}</ref>，为IPv4用户或无法接入IPv6网络的用户通过隧道提供IPv6服务。该公司提供了针对IPv6教育及培训的证书。<ref>{{cite web|last=Deploy360 Programme|title=Training: Hurricane Electric Free IPv6 Certification|url=http://www.internetsociety.org/deploy360/resources/hurricane-electric-free-ipv6-certification/|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120703053859/https://www.internetsociety.org/deploy360/resources/hurricane-electric-free-ipv6-certification/|archivedate=2012-07-03|accessdate=2016-08-30}}</ref>
通过[[互联网交换中心|互联网交换中心]]，HE.net 还提供免费的 IPv6 Transit。

